attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Gary Greene -

data.description: Escape the city life and live in peace & quiet on 9.137 acres! Located within the boundaries of Sam Houston National Forest and only 25 miles to Lake Conroe. Nature lovers will feel right at home in this charming brick home with breakfast room views of fruit trees & expansive acreage. Meticulously maintained with four spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms, this home is the perfect family retreat. Huge 30 x 40 shop for all your storage needs. Once you drive the tree lined driveway, you’ll never want to leave. No HOA!
